OL,3,CMayor promises buses will run 'not for
OL,4,Cprofit but for passengers'
OL,6,FBus services in the Liverpool City
OL,7,FRegion (LCR) are to be brought back
OL,8,Funder local control later this year
OL,9,Fafter the authority appointed two new
OL,10,Foperators.
OL,12,FMetro Mayor Steve Rotheram signed an
OL,13,Fagreement on Friday 23 January for
OL,14,Fpublicly controlled services in Wirral
OL,15,Fand St Helens for the first time since
OL,16,F1985.
