OL,3,CMayor promises buses will run 'not for
OL,4,Cprofit but for passengers'
OL,6,FFrom Autumn 2026, the LCR Combined
OL,7,FAuthority will be able to set routes,
OL,8,Ffares and timetables in the two
OL,9,Fboroughs. Further boroughs are
OL,10,Fexpected to join up in 2027.
OL,12,FIt described the move as "one of the
OL,13,Fbiggest shifts in local transport
OL,14,Fpolicy in a generation."
OL,16,FMayor Rotheram decided in 2023 to
OL,17,Ffranchise bus services in the city
OL,18,Fregion as part of a scheme which he
OL,19,Fhopes will deliver a more reliable,
OL,20,Fbetter connected network build around
OL,21,Fpassengers' needs.
