OL,3,CMayor promises buses will run 'not for
OL,4,Cprofit but for passengers'
OL,6,FFollowing a competitive tender
OL,7,Fprocess, Stagecoach has been selected
OL,8,Fto operate the franchised bus network
OL,9,Fbased in St Helens, whilst Go-Ahead
OL,10,Fwill operate in Wirral.
OL,12,FThe agreement comes twelve months
OL,13,Fafter the completion of plans to bring
OL,14,Fall buses in Greater Manchester back
OL,15,Funder public control as part of the
OL,16,FBee Network and makes the LCR the
OL,17,Fsecond area outside of London to take
OL,18,Fback control of services.
