OL,3,CMayor promises buses will run 'not for
OL,4,Cprofit but for passengers'
OL,6,FMayor Rotheram said, "We can put the
OL,7,Fpublic back into public transport, and
OL,8,Fwe can do it not for profit or for
OL,9,Fpassengers.
OL,11,F"In some cases there will be Sunday
OL,12,Fservices that don't (currently) exist
OL,13,F(and) later night services.
OL,15,F"That's because it will be publicly
OL,16,Fcontrolled and it will be us, not the
OL,17,Fbus operated companies, who decide on
OL,18,Fwhat happens on our bus system."
