OL,3,CMayor promises buses will run 'not for
OL,4,Cprofit but for passengers'
OL,6,FMayor Rotheram said the scheme
OL,7,Frepresents a "huge investment" from
OL,8,Fthe combined authority, which is
OL,9,Fbuying depots from operators and
OL,10,Fpurchasing up to 500 buses over the
OL,11,Fnext year, including more than 100 new
OL,12,Fall-electric double-deckers.
OL,14,FHundreds of millions of pounds are
OL,15,Fbeing invested in the scheme, which
OL,16,Fcomes on the back of #1.6bn transport
OL,17,Ffunding settlement secured from
OL,18,Fgovernment to help deliver new rail
OL,19,Fstations, walking and cycling routes
OL,20,Fand a new rapid transit system.
