OL,3,CMayor promises buses will run 'not for
OL,4,Cprofit but for passengers'
OL,6,FThe Metro system's yellow look,
OL,7,Freminiscent of the Bee Network, will
OL,8,Funify buses with a #500m fleet of new
OL,9,Ftrains and the building of the first
OL,10,FMersey Ferry in more than 60 years.
OL,12,FSmart ticketing will also become
OL,13,Favailable across the whole transport
OL,14,Fnetwork, the mayor added.
OL,16,FA new express service to Liverpool
OL,17,FJohn Lennon Airport will be launched
OL,18,Fin St Helens, while in Wirral routes
OL,19,Fare being extended to provide better
OL,20,Fdirect links to important destinations.
