OL,6,FCllr Paula Basnett, Leader of Wirral
OL,7,FCouncil, said: "Residents will benefit
OL,8,Ffrom stronger connections to
OL,9,Fhospitals, rail stations and services
OL,10,Fthat support both our local economy
OL,11,Fand our ambitions for a cleaner, more
OL,12,Fsustainable transport system."
