OL,3,CMayor promises buses will run 'not for
OL,4,Cprofit but for passengers'
OL,6,FCllr Anthony Burns, leader of St
OL,7,FHelens Council said: "Bus franchising
OL,8,Fis an example of devolution in action
OL,9,Fand how, as a City Region, we are
OL,10,Fdelivering for our residents,
OL,11,Fbusinesses and the environment. I am
OL,12,Fdelighted that the people of St Helens
OL,13,FBorough will be among the first to
OL,14,Fbenefit."
OL,16,FIn December it was revealed that 20
OL,17,Fbuses, running on hydrogen as part of
OL,18,Fa government trial, would be converted
OL,19,Fto battery power because of "global
OL,20,Fhydrogen supply and pricing."
